------------------------------------------------------------------------------
NOTE ON THE DATA: All CSV datasets in this repository are FULLY SYNTHETIC and
were generated by the scripts here. They do not contain, and do not derive
from, any real patient data. They are calibrated to published summary
statistics of the IMbrave150 trial (Finn RS et al., N Engl J Med 2020;
382:1894-1905) for TEACHING purposes only, and must not be used to make any
clinical or scientific claim about the actual therapies.
